title: Brandon Kyle Goodman
itunes:title: Brandon Kyle Goodman
description:
Whitney has a hot take on Elon Musk and then talks to actor, writer, and activist Brandon Kyle Goodman (Big Mouth, Modern Love).  Brandon and Whitney (with her misplaced hair extensions) talk about unhinged Etsy purchases, Queer representation, and meth head focus groups.  Brandon's The Latrell Show premieres May 23 and streams through June 20.  Get your tickets at at www.iamatheatre.com.
